Big Brother Naija, BBNaija 2020 housemate Lucy on Thursday admitted that she is attracted to Praise. Lucy made this known during her diary session with Tolanibaj who stood in as Big Brother. When asked who she is attracted to, Lucy said Praise. She, however, said she cannot be in a relationship with him in the house because of his circumstances outside the house. Praise is engaged and has a son. “If I was to pick a romantic partner it would be Praise, I’m attracted to him but due to circumstances outside the house we can’t be together.”